 void UploadClient.createNewPage(Page page, CompletionCallback<java.lang.Integer> callback)
          Creates a new page at the end of the document that the client is bound too ( UploadClient.initialize(int, CompletionCallback) must be called first) but does NOT upload any photos.

          Loads document listing for current user.
 void UploadClient.initialize(int documentId, CompletionCallback<java.lang.Void> callback)
          Initialises the upload client and binds to the given document, this will fail if the client detects any changes to the html forms hosted on the server.
 void UploadClient.login(java.lang.String username, java.lang.String password, CompletionCallback<java.lang.String> callback)
          Logs into the CGOAB server.
 void UploadClient.logout(CompletionCallback<java.lang.Void> callback)
          Logs out of the server, does nothing if not already logged in.
